OL,3,CGovernment's plans to boost workers'
OL,4,Crights to be unveiled
OL,6,FThe Government will today announce
OL,7,Fdetails of new rights for workers,
OL,8,Fincluding plans to ban exploitative
OL,9,Fzero-hours contracts and
OL,10,F"unscrupulous" fire and rehire
OL,11,Fpractices which it said will benefit
OL,12,Fmillions of workers.
OL,14,FMinisters described the Employment
OL,15,FRights Bill as the biggest boost to
OL,16,Fpay and productivity in the workplace
OL,17,Fin a generation.
