OL,6,FThere will be consultations on a new
OL,7,Fstatutory period, with ministers
OL,8,Fpromising employers a "lighter touch"
OL,9,Fprocess covering dismissals.
OL,11,FThe Bill also spells out day one
OL,12,Frights for paternity, parental and
OL,13,Fbereavement leave for millions of
OL,14,Fworkers, while statutory sick pay will
OL,15,Fbe paid from the first day of a worker
OL,16,Fbeing sick rather than having to wait
OL,17,Funtil the fourth day.
